    "description": "Vibrantly coloured roasted carrot and beetroot, tangy feta and fibre-rich bulgur, topped with pumpkin seeds and a zippy citrus dressing: our rainbow salad is packed with wholesome goodness and lots of punchy flavour. A deliciously satisfying meal that's sure to brighten your day!",
